thread.title: Florida Senate to vote on gun control, arming teachers

title: Florida Senate to vote on gun control, arming teachers
text:
Florida Senate to vote on gun control, arming teachers 1:20pm EST - 01:36 
Florida's Senate is set to vote on overhauling the state's gun laws in response to the Parkland school shooting, including a proposal to train and arm teachers and raising the minimum age for buying guns to 21.
